Title: Relates to confidentiality of records in proceedings to vacate convictions for offenses resulting from sex or labor trafficking and compelling prostitution
Summary: Provides for confidentiality of records in proceedings to vacate convictions for offenses resulting from sex or labor trafficking and compelling prostitution.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the criminal procedure law, in relation to confidentiality of records in proceedings to vacate convictions for offenses resulting from sex trafficking, labor trafficking and compelling prostitution
